OL,3,CThe defective block crisis that's
OL,4,Ccausing Ireland's homes to crumble
OL,6,FA high profile defective block
OL,7,Fcampaigner in Donegal has been forced
OL,8,Fto demolish his family home near
OL,9,FCarndonagh.
OL,11,FA problem that has effected thousands
OL,12,Fof households across Ireland.
OL,14,FPaddy Diver says despite the
OL,15,Fdestruction of his family home, he's
OL,16,Fone of the luckier householders
OL,17,Faffected as thousands more can't
OL,18,Fafford to rebuild their homes due to
OL,19,Fproblems with the Irish Government
OL,20,Fredress scheme.
