OL,3,CThe defective block crisis that's
OL,4,Ccausing Ireland's homes to crumble
OL,6,FHe continued, "It's heartbreaking, our
OL,7,Fhouses are deteriorating here but so
OL,8,Fis the insides of our heart, our
OL,9,Fmental health.
OL,11,FOur anxiety levels are going through
OL,12,Fthe roof, the depression is going
OL,13,Fthrough the roof."
OL,15,FWhat's happening is widely known as
OL,16,Fthe Mica crisis, but new research
OL,17,Fstrongly suggests that pyrite is the
OL,18,Fmineral causing the damage to the
OL,19,Fhouses.
