OL,3,CThe defective block crisis that's
OL,4,Ccausing Ireland's homes to crumble
OL,6,FMica and pyrite are minerals found in
OL,7,Fthe ground and in rocks that are
OL,8,Fexcavated from quarries and used in
OL,9,Fbuilding blocks.
OL,11,FIf too much is used, these minerals
OL,12,Fcause defects in building blocks which
OL,13,Flead to crumbling and eventually cause
OL,14,Fthe defective blocks to crack.
OL,16,FSome blocks tested have had nine times
OL,17,Fthe recommended pyrite levels.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G3/6
