OL,3,CThe defective block crisis that's
OL,4,Ccausing Ireland's homes to crumble
OL,6,FProfessor Paul Dunlop from Ulster
OL,7,FUniversity and also an affected
OL,8,Fhomeowner presented this research to
OL,9,Fan international conference in Canada.
OL,11,F"Looking around my community, seeing
OL,12,Fthe devastation that was caused, it
OL,13,Fwas a natural thing for me to step up
OL,14,Fand do because it was something that I
OL,15,Fcould sort of give back to the
OL,16,Fcommunity to try and understand what's
OL,17,Fhappening."
