OL,3,CThe defective block crisis that's
OL,4,Ccausing Ireland's homes to crumble
OL,6,FThe Irish government did introduce a
OL,7,Fmultibillion euro redress scheme, but
OL,8,Fcampaigners say it isn't fit for
OL,9,Fpurpose.
OL,11,FThey claim it's difficult to access
OL,12,Fand doesn't meet the full cost of
OL,13,Frebuilds needed.
OL,15,FAli Farran from the 100% Redress Party
OL,16,Fhas taken a political path.
OL,18,FHe is lobbying for a better scheme,
OL,19,F100% redress and to bring the
OL,20,Fcommunities put back together again.
