OL,6,FHowever, the Irish government says the
OL,7,Fenhanced grant scheme has over 2000
OL,8,Fapplications, but so far there have
OL,9,Fbeen fewer than 50 rebuilds.
OL,11,FAnd with more than 7000 homes
OL,12,Faffected, this is a crisis with no end
OL,13,Fin sight.
